00:09:59.360 --> 00:10:01.310 align:middle line:84%
Those can switch
on or off genes.

00:10:01.310 --> 00:10:04.550 align:middle line:84%
And those, in some
cases, can be inherited.

00:10:04.550 --> 00:10:06.890 align:middle line:84%
But now the taboo's
been lifted, there's

00:10:06.890 --> 00:10:08.750 align:middle line:84%
a fascinating set
